{"tid":556262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(港女勿入)廿歲美女大學生 10萬現鈔摺玫瑰花賀男友生日","createTime":"2018-02-10T11:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T10:51:03.000Z","uid":15440,"like":25,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5638de0e0a23feace5dfeb56ca52a3e8743f192b","tid":556262,"uid":15440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T11:00:58.000Z","msg":"泰國一名女大學生向男友送上用10萬泰銖（約2.47萬港元）現鈔摺的玫瑰花束，實行講心又講金。<br />\n<br />\n20歲的披拉叻表示，男友生日想要「男性化的禮物」，令她費煞思量。披拉叻在Instagram見到有人用銀紙摺花束，於是照辦煮碗，花4,000泰銖（約987港元）請人用每張面值500泰銖（約124港元）的現鈔摺玫瑰花，再集成花束送給男友做生日及情人節禮物。披拉叻表示，這些錢是她在網上賣化妝品賺回來的。<br />\n<br />\n當晚男友與一眾男性朋友在餐廳共晉晚膳，穿上性感露背低胸衣物的披拉叻，捧著花束腳踏4吋高跟鞋跑入餐廳，為男友送上驚喜。只見男友接過花束笑到「見牙唔見眼」，就知道他非常滿意這份厚禮。披拉叻表示，男友感到非常意外，也感到高興，並說即使她只是送個生日蛋糕，也會一樣很高興。<br />\n<br />\n泰國《世界日報》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180210/57815476\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180210%2F57815476&d=7CmMtxS%2FPglJXzgFmwdMUzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=96e44d6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180210%2F57815476&h=e9a82c86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180210/57815476</a>"},{"pid":"7b3d87e844f6c773e634a4293c8770aad3f36d45","tid":556262,"uid":76776,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T11:02:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2fb6ff797302ab7ee1e16f4b35934dbadb038d01","tid":556262,"uid":142872,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T11:03:07.000Z","msg":"天牙! 典解牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee040247fc905c037c59763f9f1014ef406f96e6","tid":556262,"uid":15440,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T11:04:56.000Z","msg":"港女偷偷留下負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoj